graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.19+<br/>Required]
    TrustyAI -->|routes & OAuth| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.6+<br/>Optional]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics CRD| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>Optional]
    TrustyAI -->|cert mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]
    TrustyAI -->|data storage| Database[PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|payload injection| KServe[KServe]
    TrustyAI -->|env vars config| ModelMesh[Model Mesh]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics export| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|route discovery| TrustyAI
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|integration| TrustyAI

    %% Integration Points - Data Flow
    KServe -->|inference payloads| TrustyAI
    ModelMesh -->|model payloads| TrustyAI
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| TrustyAI

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
    TrustyAI -->|OAuth validation| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP]
    TrustyAI -->|external routing| Router[OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP]

    %% Storage Options
    TrustyAI -->|PVC storage| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Default: 1Gi]
    TrustyAI -.->|database mode| DatabaseService[Database Service<br/>3306/5432]

    %% Styling
    style TrustyAI fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies (gray)
    style Kubernetes fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OpenShift fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style PrometheusOp fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Database fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI (green)
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    %% Infrastructure (orange)
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style OAuthServer fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Router fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style PVC fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style DatabaseService fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
